# Upload button scoped to document label — works for all upload button structures on summary page.
# {label} replaced at runtime with first 40 chars of the document type label text.
# Matches mat-card-content OR any ancestor row container that owns both the label <p> and Upload button.
iNRCISYFUploadBtn                   = //*[.//p[contains(normalize-space(),'{label}')] and .//button[.//span[normalize-space()='Upload']]]//button[.//span[normalize-space()='Upload']]
